parameters.command: =icav2 projectdata get "/output_folder/" --project-id {{ $('Set Project ID').item.json.PROJECT_ID }} 2>/dev/null | grep "^id" | awk '{print $2}'
=icav2 projectdata list / --project-id {{ $('Set Project ID').item.json.PROJECT_ID }} --data-type FILE 2>/dev/null | grep "fastq" | wc -l | tr -d ' '

=  INPUT_ID=$(icav2 projectdata get "/input_folder/" --project-id {{ $json.PROJECT_ID }} 2>/dev/null | grep "^id" | awk '{print $2}') && \
  OUTPUT_ID=$(icav2 projectdata get "/output_folder/" --project-id {{ $json.PROJECT_ID }} 2>/dev/null | grep "^id" | awk '{print $2}') && \
  echo "INPUT_ID=$INPUT_ID OUTPUT_ID=$OUTPUT_ID"

=  echo '{{ $json.sample_sheet_content }}' > /tmp/{{ $json.sample_sheet_filename }} && icav2 projectdata upload /tmp/{{ $json.sample_sheet_filename }} "/samplesheet_folder/{{ $json.sample_sheet_filename }}" --project-id {{
  $json.PROJECT_ID }} 2>&1 | grep "^id" | awk '{print $2}'

=PROJECT_ID='{{ $("Set Project ID").first().json.PROJECT_ID }}'

curl -s -X GET "https://ica.illumina.com/ica/rest/api/projects/${PROJECT_ID}/data?filePath=/input_folder/&type=FILE&pageSize=1000" \
    -H 'Accept: application/vnd.illumina.v3+json' \
    -H 'X-API-Key: RBsYkBubZxrPXkR3AvjLXUlYFGJJ8FOM' | \
  jq -r '.items[] | select(.data.details.name | endswith(".fastq.gz")) | select(.data.details.tags.userTags // [] | contains(["on_hold"])) | .data.details.name'

=  icav2 projectpipelines start nextflow "142fb3af-f0aa-41f2-b043-f2913671e0b4" \
    --project-id {{ $('Prepare Pipeline Launch').item.json.PROJECT_ID }} \
    --storage-size "Large" \
    --output-parent-folder {{ $json.output_folder_id }} \
    --input "run_folder:{{ $json.input_folder_id }}" \
    --input "sample_sheet:{{ $('Prepare Pipeline Launch').item.json.samplesheet_id }}" \
    --parameters "StartsFromFastq:true" \
    --user-reference "{{ $('Prepare Pipeline Launch').item.json.sample_id }}-analysis" 2>&1 | grep "^id" | awk '{print $2}'

=  echo '{{ JSON.stringify($("Prepare Pipeline Launch").item.json.files) }}' | jq -r '.[]' | while read filename; do
    FILE_ID=$(curl -s -X GET 'https://ica.illumina.com/ica/rest/api/projects/{{ $("Prepare Pipeline Launch").item.json.PROJECT_ID }}/data?filePath=/input_folder/&type=FILE&pageSize=1000' \
      -H 'Accept: application/vnd.illumina.v3+json' \
      -H 'X-API-Key: RBsYkBubZxrPXkR3AvjLXUlYFGJJ8FOM' | \
      jq -r ".items[] | select(.data.details.name == \"$filename\") | .data.id")

    if [ ! -z "$FILE_ID" ]; then
      icav2 projectdata update "$FILE_ID" --project-id {{ $("Prepare Pipeline Launch").item.json.PROJECT_ID }} --remove-user-tag "on_hold" --add-user-tag "analysis_completed" 2>&1
      echo "Updated: $filename ($FILE_ID)"
    fi
  done

=  echo '{{ JSON.stringify($("Prepare Pipeline Launch ctDNA").item.json.files) }}' | jq -r '.[]' | while read filename; do
    FILE_ID=$(curl -s -X GET 'https://ica.illumina.com/ica/rest/api/projects/{{ $("Prepare Pipeline Launch ctDNA").item.json.PROJECT_ID }}/data?filePath=/input_folder/&type=FILE&pageSize=1000' \
      -H 'Accept: application/vnd.illumina.v3+json' \
      -H 'X-API-Key: RBsYkBubZxrPXkR3AvjLXUlYFGJJ8FOM' | \
      jq -r ".items[] | select(.data.details.name == \"$filename\") | .data.id")

    if [ ! -z "$FILE_ID" ]; then
      icav2 projectdata update "$FILE_ID" --project-id {{ $("Prepare Pipeline Launch ctDNA").item.json.PROJECT_ID }} --remove-user-tag "on_hold" --add-user-tag "analysis_completed" 2>&1
      echo "Updated: $filename ($FILE_ID)"
    fi
  done

parameters.command:
=  echo '{{ $json.sample_sheet_content }}' > /tmp/{{ $json.sample_sheet_filename }} && icav2 projectdata upload /tmp/{{ $json.sample_sheet_filename }} "/samplesheet_folder/{{ $json.sample_sheet_filename }}" --project-id {{
  $json.PROJECT_ID }} 2>&1 | grep "^id" | awk '{print $2}'

=  INPUT_ID=$(icav2 projectdata get "/input_folder/{{ $json.sample_id }}/" --project-id {{ $json.PROJECT_ID }} 2>/dev/null | grep "^id" | awk '{print $2}') && \
  OUTPUT_ID=$(icav2 projectdata get "/output_folder/" --project-id {{ $json.PROJECT_ID }} 2>/dev/null | grep "^id" | awk '{print $2}') && \
  echo "INPUT_ID=$INPUT_ID OUTPUT_ID=$OUTPUT_ID"

=  icav2 projectpipelines start nextflow "850b4fe6-2a2f-4a85-ae57-cf082dfbefd4" \
    --project-id {{ $('Prepare Pipeline Launch ctDNA').item.json.PROJECT_ID }} \
    --storage-size "Large" \
    --output-parent-folder {{ $json.output_folder_id }} \
    --input "run_folder:{{ $json.input_folder_id }}" \
    --input "sample_sheet:{{ $('Prepare Pipeline Launch ctDNA').item.json.samplesheet_id }}" \
    --parameters "StartsFromFastq:true" \
    --user-reference "{{ $('Prepare Pipeline Launch ctDNA').item.json.sample_id }}-analysis" 2>&1 | grep "^id" | awk '{print $2}'
=icav2 projectdata get "/input_folder/" --project-id  {{ $('Set Project ID').item.json.PROJECT_ID }} 2>/dev/null | grep "^id" | awk '{print $2}'
=icav2 projectdata list / --project-id {{ $('Set Project ID').item.json.PROJECT_ID }} --data-type FILE --file-name .fastq.gz --match-mode FUZZY -o json 2>/dev/null

=SAMPLE_ID='{{ $json.sample_id }}'
PROJECT_ID='{{ $json.PROJECT_ID }}'
FILES='{{ JSON.stringify($json.files) }}'

echo "=== İşleniyor: $SAMPLE_ID ==="

# Klasör ID'sini list komutundan al (daha güvenilir)
SAMPLE_FOLDER_ID=$(icav2 projectdata list \
  --project-id "$PROJECT_ID" \
  --parent-folder "/input_folder/" \
  2>&1 | grep "^${SAMPLE_ID} " | awk '{print $4}')

echo "Klasör ID: $SAMPLE_FOLDER_ID"

if [ -z "$SAMPLE_FOLDER_ID" ]; then
  echo "HATA: Klasör bulunamadı, oluşturuluyor..."
  icav2 projectdata create "$SAMPLE_ID" \
    --data-type FOLDER \
    --folder-path "/input_folder/" \
    --project-id "$PROJECT_ID"
  
  # Tekrar dene
  SAMPLE_FOLDER_ID=$(icav2 projectdata list \
    --project-id "$PROJECT_ID" \
    --parent-folder "/input_folder/" \
    2>&1 | grep "^${SAMPLE_ID} " | awk '{print $4}')
fi

if [ -z "$SAMPLE_FOLDER_ID" ]; then
  echo "HATA: Klasör ID alınamadı!"
  exit 1
fi

# Dosyaları taşı
echo "$FILES" | jq -r '.[] | .file_id' | while read FILE_ID; do
  echo "Taşınıyor: $FILE_ID"
  icav2 projectdata move "$FILE_ID" \
    --destination-folder "$SAMPLE_FOLDER_ID" \
    --project-id "$PROJECT_ID" 2>&1 || echo "Taşıma hatası (belki zaten orada)"
done

# Dosyaları etiketle
echo "$FILES" | jq -r '.[] | .file_id' | while read FILE_ID; do
  echo "Etiketleniyor: $FILE_ID"
  icav2 projectdata update "$FILE_ID" \
    --add-user-tag on_hold \
    --project-id "$PROJECT_ID"
done

echo "✓ Tamamlandı: $SAMPLE_ID ($(echo $FILES | jq '. | length') dosya)"

=  echo '{{ $json.sample_sheet_content }}' > /tmp/{{ $json.sample_sheet_filename }} && icav2 projectdata upload /tmp/{{ $json.sample_sheet_filename }} "/samplesheet_folder/{{ $json.sample_sheet_filename }}" --project-id {{
  $json.PROJECT_ID }} 2>&1 | grep "^id" | awk '{print $2}'

=  icav2 projectpipelines start nextflow "506f136e-980e-427d-ab39-f91654255bea" \
    --project-id {{ $('Prepare Pipeline Launch HRD').item.json.PROJECT_ID }} \
    --storage-size "Large" \
    --output-parent-folder {{ $('Loop Over Items HRD').item.json.output_folder_id }} \
    --input "run_folder:{{ $('Loop Over Items HRD').item.json.input_folder_id }}" \
    --input "sample_sheet:{{ $('Prepare Pipeline Launch HRD').item.json.samplesheet_id }}" \
    --parameters "StartsFromFastq:true" \
    --user-reference "{{ $('Prepare Pipeline Launch HRD').item.json.sample_id }}-analysis" 2>&1 | grep "^id" | awk '{print $2}'

=  echo '{{ JSON.stringify($("Prepare Pipeline Launch HRD").item.json.files) }}' | jq -r '.[]' | while read filename; do
    FILE_ID=$(curl -s -X GET 'https://ica.illumina.com/ica/rest/api/projects/{{ $("Prepare Pipeline Launch HRD").item.json.PROJECT_ID }}/data?filePath=/input_folder/&type=FILE&pageSize=1000' \
      -H 'Accept: application/vnd.illumina.v3+json' \
      -H 'X-API-Key: RBsYkBubZxrPXkR3AvjLXUlYFGJJ8FOM' | \
      jq -r ".items[] | select(.data.details.name == \"$filename\") | .data.id")

    if [ ! -z "$FILE_ID" ]; then
      icav2 projectdata update "$FILE_ID" --project-id {{ $("Prepare Pipeline Launch HRD").item.json.PROJECT_ID }} --remove-user-tag "on_hold" --add-user-tag "analysis_completed" 2>&1
      echo "Updated: $filename ($FILE_ID)"
    fi
  done
